            <noteGrp type="workDesc">
               <note type="description">Treatise on creation of spirits, Pen, Throne, the heavens
                     and ranks of angels. Books mentioned in text are K. al-Nikāḥ (RG 544), K.
                     al-Nafs (RG 521?) and al-Durra al-bayḍāʾ.</note>
               <note type="structure"/>
               <note type="contentsNote"/>
